Bale: When asked about a potential return to the Premier League, he said: &quot;I need to be playing week in week out and that hasn't happened this season for one reason or another.<br />
<br />
Ronaldo: &quot;I'm not saying I'm going, in the coming days we will see. They took something out of context that I shouldn't have said. I didn't know it'd be so strong. I prefer not to talk and to enjoy this lovely moment to the maximum.&quot;
